    • Method Detail

      • getDefaultColorTable

        public static ColorTable8 getDefaultColorTable(int c)
        Gets the color table corresponding to a default channel ordering of RGBCMY. Channels beyond the sixth are assigned the grayscale color table.

      • isGrayColorTable

        public static boolean isGrayColorTable(ColorTable table)
        Tests whether a ColorTable consists of gray values. A gray table does not have to be a ramp.
